Class CombinedChart

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.jrefinery.chart.JFreeChart
        |
        +--com.jrefinery.chart.combination.CombinedChart
All Implemented Interfaces:
DatasetChangeListener, JFreeChartConstants, JFreeChartInfo, LegendChangeListener, PlotChangeListener, TitleChangeListener
public class CombinedChart
extends JFreeChart

A CombinedChart can be added to a CombinedPlot. Many of the facilities inherited from JFreeChart aren't needed, so the event handling methods are overidden with empty methods.

See Also:
CombinedPlot
